The notes on MHS replace the bulletin boards and mail systems found on many
other sleds.  There are several types of notes including In-Character notes 
(inotes), Out-of-Character Notes(onotes), Bug Notes (bug), Quest Notes (qnotes) 
and God Notes (gnote). 
The following options are usable (in this case, an inote is used as an example,
for other types of notes, simply replace inote with the appropriate type of
note):

reading notes:
inote list    : show all inotes (unread notes are marked with an N)
inote read    : either by number, or read next to read unread inotes
inote remove  : removes an inote that you wrote or are the target of
inote catchup : markes all inotes as read
spool         : Catches up all notes of all types
unread        : Lists notes that have not been read by this character

writing new notes:
inote to      : sets the to line (name, clanname, 'clans', immortal, or all)
inote subject : sets the subject for a new inote
inote +       : adds a line to a new inote (i.e. inote + hi guys!)
inote ++      : adds two lines to a new inote (i.e. a new paragraph)
