0 ALLY ALLIANCE~
None~
0 1 none
Syntax: ally <clan> <duration> <payment> <bribe>
Syntax: ally <clan> <accept/reject>

clan: The clan you want to ally with, or that has offered an alliance to you.
duration: How long, in days, the alliance will last.  From 1 to 7.  The longer
  the duration, the more tribute must be paid to make the alliance.
payment: Who will be paying.  Options: Full, Split.  Full means the offering
  clan pays the entire price, split means 50/50 between the two clans.
bribe: Optional bribe, in tribute points, that may be up to five times the
  payment amount.  If the alliance is accepted, the recipient will claim the
  bribe.

Offering an alliance costs 5 points of tribute immediately.  If the alliance is
accepted, that 5 points is counted towards costs already paid.  If it is not,
those points are lost.  The offer will be valid for 24 hours from the time it
is made, then it will be automatically rejected.

Usage: To form an alliance, one clan leader initiates, then a receiving leader
  accepts.  So if the clan "Prey" wanted to offer an alliance to the clan
  "Hunters" and was willing to bribe them 200 points, their leader could enter:
  ally hunters 7 full 200 and a Hunters leader could then decide to 'ally prey
  accept' or 'ally prey reject' based on if that 200 point bribe was worth a
  week of not hunting them.  If the Hunters accepted, the Prey clan would pay
  an additional 100 points for the week of alliance (300 total, due to the
  bribe).  If the Hunters refuse, the Prey clan would still pay 5 points for
  having made the offer.

Effect: When allied, you may group regardless of normal clan type restrictions.
  You are also prevented from attacking allies.

Costs: 1 day:  16 points of tribute.
       2 days: 30 points of tribute.
       3 days: 44 points of tribute.
       4 days: 58 points of tribute.
       5 days: 72 points of tribute.
       6 days: 86 points of tribute.
       7 days: 100 points of tribute.

If at least one of the clans is type Peace, the cost is 4 points less per day
of the alliance - so it goes from 12 (-4) to 72 (-28) points for 1 to 7 days.

Also see:
help clan peace
