Building your hall is done in two steps.  First, you create the new feature
that you want to add.  You will be told the cost to load this item, and can
review all the descriptions on it to ensure that it is what you want.  When
you decide you are ready and your clan has enough tribute, you can request
that your new feature be added.

Be careful to only load objects you want added into the rooms you want them
in, because while there is a refund when you remove something it is not the
full value.  You can upgrade NPCs that have been placed without having to
remove them.

To build the hall itself, you must be a leader of the clan or have been given
permission by the leaders.  Not all functions of building may be available to
you in your hall.

You may also have the opportunity to build personal rooms.  To have personal
rooms requires that you be a member of a clan (So you have a place to attach
your room to), and costs for the room will come out of your bank account.  {YThe
personal rooms feature is not currently available, but will be enabled in the
future.{x

