1363837675 4 Andaron
Capsules are items that can contain other items.  Setting up a capsule is
fairly straightforward.  Once you've set the item type, to control what
the capsule drops when opened you set its values:
 
Value 0: Amount of xp to award, from 0 to 1000.
Value 1: Amount of silver to award, from 0 to 110000. This will convert to
  gold when appropriate (120 silver = 1 gold 20 silver)
Value 2: Amount of skill points to award, from 0 to 5.
Value 3: Vnum of item to award, 0 for no item.
Value 4: Variance % for xp and silver, from 0 to 100. 0 will always give
  the exact amount for xp and silver, while 100 will go anywhere from 0
  to 200% the amount (It does plus and minus the input %). Standard value
  if you want variance is 5-10%.
 
Be responsible with your rewards and don't put the bigger values on things
when not appropriate. While almost any vnum may be contained in a capsule
the item slot is mostly meant for gems or other such trinkets.
 
Note that a capsule is not a valid item to have in a capsule.
~
